threats.title: Compromised service account
threats.description: Compromised account through phishing or social engineering

threats.title: DDoS attack
threats.description: DDoS attack involving high amount of requests to the web server
threats.mitigation:
Firewall with DDoS protection
Load balancers

threats.title: Privilege escalation of compromised account
threats.mitigation: Provide remediation for this threat or a reason if status is N/A

threats.title: Executing system functions with compromised accounts
threats.description: Using the compromised account, the attacker executes other functions of the system
threats.mitigation:
System RBAC with PLoP
Endpoint Detection and Response (EDR)
Malware prevention with IDS/IPS

threats.title: Escalate privileges to OS admin
threats.description: Using the compromised service account, the attacker attempts to execute OS level functions
threats.mitigation: Privileged Access Management (PAM) with Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)

threats.title: Data exfiltration
threats.description: Data exiltration due to account abuse
threats.mitigation:
Database activity monitoring
Database RBAC with PoLP

threats.title: Unauthorized data manipulation
threats.description: Unauthorized data manipulation due to privilege abuse
threats.mitigation:
Database activity monitoring
Audit logging and SIEM
